This is my vim config

If you want to use it, symlink vimrc to your ~/.vimrc and the whole directory
to ~/.vim

less and scss files use the css syntax highlighting

snipMate is installed, see the snippets directory to known what it can do

Current mapping:
general
,l	display unprintable caracters

ruby
,j	open taglist view

eruby
<C-_>   complete latest opened xml/html tag

html 
<C-_>   complete latest opened xml/html tag

xml
<C-_>   complete latest opened xml/html tag
